{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, if the LLMs cannot handle these fundamental tasks, they are unlikely to be able to conduct any of the more advanced tasks required of lawyers.",
    "1.1 Large language models and their use in legal contexts",
    "LLMs are advanced AI systems that process human language (referred to as \"natural language\" in this context).",
    "This means they can generate and respond to human text, with recent systems appearing to be capable of doing this in a manner that is nearimperceptibly distinct from humans.",
    "The state of the art employs a deep learning technique called the Transformer architecture to accomplish this (Topal et al. 2021)."
  ]
}